OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773396299
OL,3,CRobbers stole #50,000 of phones from
OL,4,Cshopping centre in 'terrifying ordeal'
OL,6,FThree robbers who stole #50,000 worth
OL,7,Fof mobile phones and electrical
OL,8,Fdevices from a shopping centre in
OL,9,FSittingbourne have been convicted.
OL,11,FIonut Calin entered the store with
OL,12,FDobre Vasile-Iosif and Valentin
OL,13,FCiuraru, and threatened staff at The
OL,14,FForum Shopping Centre in the High
OL,15,FStreet, before demanding they open the
OL,16,Fsafe where the phones were kept, then
OL,17,Fthey got away in a waiting vehicle.
OL,19,FWorkers managed to track them down 11
OL,20,Fmiles away hiding in bushes in
OL,21,FGillingham Park.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
