PN,41802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773396299
OL,3,CRobbers stole #50,000 of phones from
OL,4,Cshopping centre in 'terrifying ordeal'
OL,6,FThe bags of phones were also located.
OL,8,FCalin, 23, from Milton Road,
OL,9,FGillingham, Vasile-Iosif, 19, from
OL,10,FHarrow Road, London and Ciuraru, 25,
OL,11,Ffrom Central Park Road, London were
OL,12,Farrested and charged with robbery.
OL,14,FCalin admitted to the offence at an
OL,15,Fearlier court hearing and at Maidstone
OL,16,FCrown Court on Monday 9 March 2026 was
OL,17,Fjailed for two years and three months.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
