PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773396299
OL,3,CRobbers stole #50,000 of phones from
OL,4,Cshopping centre in 'terrifying ordeal'
OL,6,FVasile-Iosif and Ciuraru were bailed
OL,7,Fby the court pending a trial but were
OL,8,Ffound guilty in their absence after
OL,9,Ffailing to attend.
OL,11,FA warrant has been issued for their
OL,12,Farrests.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
