PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773396299
OL,3,CRobbers stole #50,000 of phones from
OL,4,Cshopping centre in 'terrifying ordeal'
OL,6,FInvestigating officer Detective
OL,7,FConstable Scott Bittlestone said: "The
OL,8,Fstaff at the store were put through a
OL,9,Fterrifying ordeal but thanks to their
OL,10,Fswift actions and the coordinated
OL,11,Fresponse from our officers, we were
OL,12,Fable to bring Calin to justice and
OL,13,Frecover thousands of pounds' worth of
OL,14,Fstolen goods."
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
